🌦️ Weather App


A simple and elegant Weather Application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript that fetches real-time weather data from the OpenWeatherMap API.

This app displays the current temperature, weather description, and weather icon for a specific city (default: Delhi).

🚀 Features

🌍 Real-time weather data using OpenWeatherMap API

🌡️ Displays temperature (in Celsius)

☁️ Shows weather condition (e.g., cloudy, sunny, rainy)

🗺️ Displays location name with a map marker icon

🔁 Refresh button to reload weather data

🎨 Clean and modern Neumorphic UI design

📱 Fully responsive layout

🧠 Tech Stack
Technology	Purpose

HTML5	Structure of the app

CSS3	Styling and layout

JavaScript	Fetching data from the API and DOM manipulation

OpenWeatherMap API	Provides live weather data

Font Awesome	Icons (map marker, refresh, etc.)

Google Fonts (Poppins)	Font styling
